()Role Hierarchy kya hai?
Definition: Ye roles ko ek hierarchy (parent-child relationship) me organize karna hai,
jisse higher-level role automatically lower-level roles ke permissions inherit kar sake.
Purpose:-
Access management simplify karna
Reuse aur consistency maintain karna
Audit aur compliance easy karna

2️⃣ Example of Role Hierarchy:-
Business Role: Senior Manager
   ├── Role: Manager
   │      ├── Role: Team Lead
   │      │      └── Role: Employee
   
4️⃣ Code Example (Conceptual):-
Identity rahul = getIdentity("EMP12345");

